long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The OpenLayer extension allows users to participate in the OpenLayer ecosystem by contributing their computing resources, network bandwidth as well as personal data and knowledge. Users can complete daily tasks, track their progress, invite friends, as well as tracking their OpenLayer AVS points acquired through staking in OpenLayer AVS.
